description: We are excited to announce that the submissions for the 8th issue of the Delta Epsilon Undergraduate Math Journal are now open! We are a student-run publication for undergraduate students to experience the academic research and publication process. Our journal is peer-reviewed by a team of graduate students. The detailed submission guidelines can be found on our website (link in our bio), where you can also explore old issues if you'd like. Any McGill undergraduate is invited to submit, regardless of your program. We are looking for all kinds of articles, ranging from research papers to historical pieces to recreational games and puzzles. Don't hesitate to reach out with any questions! The deadline to submit will be January 31st, 2025 at 11:59pm. Submissions can be emailed to thedeltaepsilon@gmail.com.
